<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Knights Frontier – 회원정보 수정</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #040818;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1280px;
      padding: 32px 24px 40px;
    }

    header {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    header img {
      height: 110px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .header-actions {
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .header-btn {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: 1px solid #8fa3ff;
      background: transparent;
      color: #e2e7ff;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.15s ease-out, color 0.15s ease-out,
        border-color 0.15s ease-out;
    }

    .header-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(143, 163, 255, 0.22);
    }

    .content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .card {
      background: #dde5f5;
      color: #1a2438;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 580px;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #1a2438;
    }

    .page-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #5a6c7d;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .form-label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .form-label .required {
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin-left: 3px;
    }

    .form-input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 2px solid #b8c5d6;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #1a2438;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    .form-input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #4a6bff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(74, 107, 255, 0.15);
    }

    .form-input:disabled {
      background: #e8ecf1;
      color: #7f8c9a;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .form-hint {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7f8c9a;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .password-section {
      background: #f4f7fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .password-section-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .button-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 2px solid #c8d4e3;
    }

    .btn {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s ease-out, transform 0.08s ease-out;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #27ae60;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #2ecc71;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-primary:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #95a5a6;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #b4bec0;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .info-box {
      background: #fff9e6;
      border-left: 4px solid #f1c40f;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .info-box-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #8e6b02;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .info-box-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b5a0f;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page {
        padding: 24px 16px 32px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 24px 20px;
      }

      header {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .header-actions {
        position: static;
        margin-left: auto;
      }

      .button-group {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <div class="header-actions">
        <a href="/main" class="header-btn">대시보드</a>
        <a href="/mypage" class="header-btn">마이페이지</a>
      </div>

      <img src="logo_1.png" alt="Knights Frontier 로고" />
    </header>

    <main class="content">
      <section class="card">
        <h1 class="page-title">회원정보 수정</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">회원님의 정보를 안전하게 관리하세요</p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="info-box-title">⚠️ 보안 안내</div>
          <div class="info-box-text">
            비밀번호를 변경하지 않으려면 해당 필드를 비워두세요.
          </div>
        </div>

        <form id="edit-profile-form" method="POST" action="/api/users/update-profile">

          <!-- 닉네임 -->
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label">
              닉네임<span class="required">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-input"
              name="nickname"
              value="<%= user.nickname %>"
              placeholder="닉네임을 입력하세요"
              required
            />
            <div class="form-hint">2-20자 이내로 입력해주세요.</div>
          </div>

          <!-- 이메일 -->
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label">
              이메일<span class="required">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="email"
              class="form-input"
              name="email"
              value="<%= user.email %>"
              placeholder="email@example.com"
              required
            />
            <div class="form-hint">알림을 받을 이메일 주소입니다.</div>
          </div>

          <!-- 비밀번호 변경 섹션 -->
          <div class="password-section">
            <div class="password-section-title">비밀번호 변경</div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">현재 비밀번호</label>
              <input
                type="password"
                class="form-input"
                name="current_password"
                placeholder="현재 비밀번호를 입력하세요"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">새 비밀번호</label>
              <input
                type="password"
                class="form-input"
                name="new_password"
                placeholder="새 비밀번호를 입력하세요"
              />
              <div class="form-hint">8자 이상, 영문/숫자/특수문자 조합</div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
              <label class="form-label">새 비밀번호 확인</label>
              <input
                type="password"
                class="form-input"
                name="confirm_password"
                placeholder="새 비밀번호를 다시 입력하세요"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 버튼 -->
          <div class="button-group">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="history.back()">
              취소
            </button>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
              저장하기
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script>
    // 폼 제출 시 확인만 수행 (유효성 검사는 서버에서)
    document.getElementById('edit-profile-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      // 실제 제출 시 확인 메시지
      if (!confirm('회원정보를 수정하시겠습니까?')) {
        e.preventDefault();
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>